(64, 5, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01014010S-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		五花肉：补肾、滋阴、益气</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		黄瓜：利水、清热、解毒</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					五花肉400克（或后腿肉）</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					黄瓜1根</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					葱2-3段</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					花椒7-8粒</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					肉汤1大勺</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					黄酒20ml</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0101404Z8-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.五花肉用清水浸泡2小时泡出血水后沥干备用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01014033X-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.锅内做水，水热后（大约70度左右）下入五花肉（如有血沫析出需撇净）</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0101403Q3-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.水开后下入调料和黄酒转中小火煮制约30-40分钟，煮好后捞出晾凉放入冰箱冷藏1小时以上备用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0101403I7-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.大蒜捣成（或用压蒜器）蒜泥，加入肉汤和盐拌匀</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010140K54-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.加入剩下的调料拌匀后制成蒜泥味汁</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0101403495-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.冷藏好的白肉取出后切片儿</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0101402425-7.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.黄瓜洗净后用削皮刀削成薄片</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0101401I8-8.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.和肉片搭配卷起</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0101402143-9.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					9.装盘后淋入蒜泥味汁制作完成</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 4