(66, 5, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102404549-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		鸡蛋：润燥、增强免疫力、护眼明目</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		韭菜：温中、补肾、解毒</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		虾皮：补肾壮阳、辅助降血压、升压</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡蛋2个</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					韭菜适量</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					料酒1茶匙</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					生抽少许</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					盐适量</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					水1茶匙</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010240J48-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.韭菜择净，反复清洗之后控干水分，切3厘米左右长段装盘备用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102401334-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.虾皮用清水稍稍浸泡后捞出挤干水分，备用；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102404326-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.1茶匙玉米淀粉、1茶匙料酒和1茶匙水集中在一个碗里，混合均匀；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01024059D-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.把两个鸡蛋磕在这个碗里；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102406417-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.用筷子搅打成均匀的蛋液；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102405P7-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.起锅烧热后，倒入油，要稍稍多一些，油温六七成热时从四周淋蛋液，稍稍凝固后翻个身；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01024041Y-7.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.铲成小块出锅装进碗里备用；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010240N42-8.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.锅里还有部分底油，不需要再放油了。把盘里的韭菜段全部倒进去，快速翻炒；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102403639-9.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					9.大约10秒钟后放入鸡蛋块儿，同时放适量盐，继续快速翻炒；</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102402352-10.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					10.再10秒钟后放入虾皮，滴几滴生抽，翻炒均匀即可出锅。从韭菜下锅到最后出锅总共20多秒的时间，还真是一个考验啊！</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102404S8-11.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					11.出锅装盘，上桌开吃吧！</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0102405593-12.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					12.对于喜欢韭菜的人来说，真是无法抵挡的诱惑啊！</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			揭秘炒韭菜鸡蛋的两个关键环节：</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1、鸡蛋里要放入适量料酒、玉米淀粉和水，可有效去除鸡蛋的腥气，煎蛋会更发些，煎好的鸡蛋更软嫩；</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2、这是一道快手菜：韭菜下锅，10秒钟；盐和鸡蛋下锅，10秒钟；虾皮和生抽，5秒钟搞定。25秒钟搞定，一定要快哦！</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(67, 5, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103043153-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		青椒：增强免疫力、抗氧化、抗癌防癌</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					里脊</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					青椒</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					黑木耳</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					淀粉</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					料酒</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					糖</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					生抽</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡精</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103042317-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.准备好所有的食材，木耳提前泡发。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103043131-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.里脊肉切丝加入盐，生抽，糖，鸡精，料酒，淀粉抓拌均匀腌制片刻。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010304MP-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.泡好的木耳洗净切丝，青椒洗净切丝，葱姜切碎。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103042318-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.炒锅到油烧热倒入肉丝翻炒。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103043F7-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.炒至肉丝变色坚挺盛出备用。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010304O26-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.锅中再加少许油爆香葱姜。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103043Y4-7.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.倒入木耳和青椒翻炒。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010304IR-8.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.加入生抽和糖。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010304L57-9.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					9.再加少许盐翻炒均匀。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103044416-10.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					10.把肉丝倒入混合翻炒。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103044454-11.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					11.淋入适量的香油。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103045615-12.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					12.翻炒均匀关火。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1.肉丝要腌拌片刻入味，再炒至变色即可盛出，最后再合适他食材混合，这样炒出的肉丝香嫩适口。</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2.这是一道快手炒菜，青椒入锅加入调味料翻炒均匀即可关火，不要时间长，以免影响青椒的口感。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(68, 5, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103325N5-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		丝瓜：解毒、凉血、清热化痰</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		鸡蛋：润燥、增强免疫力、护眼明目</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					丝瓜2根</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡蛋3个</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					盐</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					油2汤匙</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					姜末</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010332I53-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.丝瓜去皮切滚刀片，如果家里没有刨子去皮的话，一般卖丝瓜的地方可以帮你去丝瓜皮的</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103324351-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.锅中烧水，水开倒入丝瓜焯水</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010332L60-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.倒入丝瓜后，水再次开就可以捞出来了。如果想使颜色保持翠绿的话，要用冷水冲凉一下</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01033233b-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.将鸡蛋打入碗中，加盐，用筷子充分搅打均匀待用。锅里放油3汤匙烧热，将鸡蛋放入锅中炒熟盛出待用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010332G44-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.锅中底油，油微热放姜末爆香，倒入焯过水的丝瓜，加盐翻炒</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010332G44-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.大火翻炒30秒后，就可以加待用的蛋花。一起混炒也不要太长时间，20－30秒也就可以出锅了</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			这是一道口清新的川菜，适合家庭聚餐。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0');
