(69, 5, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103531L9-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		百合：安神、清心、润肺</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					西芹</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					百合</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					盐</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					胡椒粉</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡精</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103534026-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.西芹洗净，斜切成小段。锅里水煮开，放入西芹焯水一分钟左右，捞出冲凉水沥干。百合去掉黑色部分，掰成小片，洗净沥干</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103531496-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.烧热锅，倒入油加热后，放焯过水的西芹，翻炒片刻</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0103534a2-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.放入百合，加盐和鸡精调味，快速翻炒入味，看到百合边缘变透明马上关火出锅</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			这是一道口清新的川菜，适合家庭聚餐。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(70, 5, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0104136063-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		荷兰豆：利水、增强免疫力、护眼明目</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					荷兰豆350g</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					大蒜20g</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食用油25ml</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食盐5g</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0104132537-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.大蒜切成蒜蓉</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010413E01-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.嫩荷兰豆择去两头的老筋</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01041351O-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.锅里烧开水</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010413I96-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.放入一点油和盐，将荷兰豆焯水</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0104135I9-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.一分钟后，将荷兰豆捞起，过凉水，沥干</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0104134632-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.锅里坐油</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0104136409-7.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.放入蒜蓉，煸香</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0104133335-8.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.倒入荷兰豆，加少许食盐，大火快炒出锅</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1.可以多加蒜蓉，用油煸香后，味道杠杠滴</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2.荷兰豆焯水时，加些油和盐，会保持荷兰豆翠绿的颜色</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			3.要大火快炒哦，因为荷兰豆已经焯过水了</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(71, 3, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01051LQ2-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		姜：降逆止呕、化痰止咳、散寒解表</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		白糖：富含碳水化合物</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					猪肉末200克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					挂面400克</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					熏干一块（约60克）</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					青菜叶6片</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					姜10克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					料酒30ml</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					花椒粉10克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					香葱</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01051J910-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.猪肉末中加入料酒15ml，盐2克一起拌匀腌制半小时。熏干切成半厘米见方的小块备用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01051L419-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.油锅加入底油烧热，放入姜末炒出香味，然后放入猪肉末炒到颜色变白</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01051J019-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.放入熏干块慢慢炒出香味，然后放入料酒、酱油炒到熏干和猪肉变成红色</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01051L413-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.放入高汤或者清水，水量没过材料1/2即可，然后加入盐、白糖煮到汤汁上色，味道变浓即可</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01051I222-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.另起一个汤锅，将水烧开后放入面条，将面条煮到约八成熟后捞出。面条盛在碗中，加入之前煮好的料，烫好的青菜，根据口味加入香醋、花椒粉、红油、芝麻、香葱拌匀即可</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			豆角加入清水后焖的时候要稍长一点，如果最后感觉豆角还是有点硬，可以再淋入一点清水。前提是一定要确保豆角完全成熟，否则容易食物中毒。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(72, 3, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0105503J7-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		红枣：安神、补脾胃、辅助降血脂</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		姜：降逆止呕、化痰止咳、散寒解表</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					土鸡半只</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡油菌500g</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					红枣6颗</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					枸杞15颗</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					姜1块</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0105505505-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.鸡斩块后，洗净沥干，生姜切片。锅中放1勺油，轻晃锅体，使油均匀分布（目的是防粘锅），下入鸡块和姜片，翻炒5分钟。（我们湖北人煨汤时习惯先把主料炒一炒，油只需放一点点，因为鸡肉在炒制的过程中也会出一部分油的）</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0105504D5-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.鸡肉炒香后，往炒锅里加入开水，水量没过鸡肉，煮开后倒入汤煲内，中火煲</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0105501P0-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.将鸡油菌去蒂，洗净，备用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01055044I-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.1小时后，下入鸡油菌和红枣，继续煲15分钟</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0105503D0-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.15分钟后，加入枸杞和盐，继续煲一刻钟即可</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(73, 3, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0106341G6-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		花生：健脾、化痰、润肺</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		莲子：养心安神、止泻、补脾</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		薏米：健脾、利湿、除痹</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					花生100克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					莲子1小把</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					薏米50克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					香芋100克</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					糯米粉100克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					冰糖1块</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					白糖1大勺</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0106346154-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.花生、莲子、薏米清洗干净，放水中浸泡一夜</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010634C25-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.砂锅中放半锅清水，将泡过的莲子、花生、薏米放入</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0106344917-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.大火烧开转小火慢慢炖煮，加入一块冰糖</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0106341A8-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.香芋去皮切片上锅蒸熟</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010634Jb-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.稍微晾凉</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0106346154-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.加入一大勺白糖，用擀面杖碾碎，和糯米粉按1:1的比例糅合成粉团</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010634C25-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.将粉团搓长条，用手揪成小块，揉成小汤圆状</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010634Jb-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.看砂锅中的花生等熟烂</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0106344917-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					9.即可将芋圆丢入</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0106341A8-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					10.等到芋圆全部浮在水面上即可关火，放凉后即可食用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(74, 3, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010A520M-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		红枣：安神、补脾胃、辅助降血脂</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		莲子：养心安神、止泻、补脾</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		百合：安神、清心、润肺</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					红枣</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					莲子</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					百合</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					瘦肉</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					大米</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					味精</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010A5B56-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.备齐原料：大米，瘦肉，百合，莲子，红枣。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010A560W-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.瘦肉洗净切丝。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010A52027-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.米淘洗干净倒入适量煮粥所需的水后去煮粥。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010A535E-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.加入莲子和红枣。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010A55238-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.待锅内的粥开锅以后加入瘦肉丝，用勺子搅拌一下继续煮。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/010A54045-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.粥煮熟后把百合倒入锅内再煮十分钟，最后加少许盐和味精调味。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1.喜欢百合煮久煮烂一点的话就跟瘦肉一起放入锅内，因为我比较喜欢吃不是很烂的，所以最后才放的。</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2.瘦肉不要太多只需一点提鲜味即可。</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			3.莲子要早一点放，因为莲子要多煮一会。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0');
