 auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.把山药放蒸屉蒸20分钟左右至熟。用筷子轻易扎透即可。取出过凉，然后切小段</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0110253G0-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.淋上糖玫瑰即可。（其他的果酱也可以的哦，比如蓝莓酱、草莓酱等）</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			无</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(80, 2, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01105361W-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		青椒：增强免疫力、抗氧化、抗癌防癌</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		花椒：温中、止泻、止痛</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					杏仁露1罐</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					小号木瓜1个</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					吉利丁片2片</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					盐适量</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0110531309-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.小号木瓜1个洗净备用，吉利丁片放入冰水中泡软</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0110535V3-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.木瓜沿着颈部切掉</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0110534158-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.用细长的小勺掏出木瓜籽</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01105315O-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.木瓜杏仁冻的做法图解44.杏仁露放入小锅中，中火加热，边缘微微冒泡离火。加入泡软的吉利丁片，迅速搅拌至融化</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011053C49-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.煮好的杏仁露稍事冷却至常温，倒入木瓜中</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0110531309-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.盖上切下来的木瓜盖子，入冰箱冷藏一晚。拿出来切块即可</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1.木瓜可以放在一个小碗中，这样就不会倒了。</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2.如果木瓜买的较大，可以增加杏仁露的用量。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(81, 2, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114T317-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		花生：健脾、化痰、润肺</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		莲子：养心安神、止泻、补脾</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		薏米：健脾、利湿、除痹</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					花生100克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					莲子1小把</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					薏米50克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					香芋100克</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					糯米粉100克</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					冰糖1块</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					白糖1大勺</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114U4L-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.花生、莲子、薏米清洗干净，放水中浸泡一夜</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114UY5-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.砂锅中放半锅清水，将泡过的莲子、花生、薏米放入</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114T054-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.大火烧开转小火慢慢炖煮，加入一块冰糖</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114WJ3-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.香芋去皮切片上锅蒸熟</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114Q3O-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.稍微晾凉</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114U4L-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.加入一大勺白糖，用擀面杖碾碎，和糯米粉按1:1的比例糅合成粉团</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114UY5-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.将粉团搓长条，用手揪成小块，揉成小汤圆状</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114Q3O-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.看砂锅中的花生等熟烂</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114T054-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					9.即可将芋圆丢入</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01114WJ3-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					10.等到芋圆全部浮在水面上即可关火，放凉后即可食用</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0');
