(82, 2, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112152014-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		姜：降逆止呕、化痰止咳、散寒解表</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		芝麻油：改善血液循环、延缓衰老、抗氧化</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					黑木耳一小把</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					青椒半个</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					姜一片</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					香醋</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					花椒3-5颗</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					芝麻油</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112153932-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.干的黑木耳提前用冷水浸泡好。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112151W2-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.泡好的黑木耳洗净后撕成小朵。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112152221-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.青椒，红椒，香葱洗净后分别切小丁，姜切丝。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112151020-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.锅中加入适量清水，烧开后将黑木耳放入绰一下，捞出控干水份。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112152V0-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.木耳及青红椒丁放在一个稍大的碗中，加入适量的盐及鸡精。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112155306-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.调入海鲜酱油。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011215H59-7.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.倒入适量的香醋。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01121541c-8.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.加入少许的芝麻油。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112152V0-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					9.锅中倒入少许色拉油，油热后将花椒炸出香味后捞出不要，关火后将香葱及白芝麻倒入爆香。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112155306-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					10.姜丝放在黑木耳的上部，用热油浇在姜丝上，拌匀即可。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1．品质好的黑木耳:朵大肉薄，表面乌黑光润背面呈淡灰色，手感较干份量轻就是质量较好的。</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2．泡黑木耳最好是用冷水慢慢泡，用开水虽快但木耳口感会比较粘软。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(83, 2, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112432Q2-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		酱油：升压、补血、护齿</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		醋：消食积、解毒、补血</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					莲藕</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					蒜</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					干辣椒碎</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					醋</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					盐适量</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					芝麻油</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112432347-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.莲藕表面刷洗干净，冷水入锅，盖上盖，煮25分钟左右至熟</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112434321-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.煮好的莲藕待不烫手时切厚片</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011243CB-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.干辣椒碎放进小碗里</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112432V9-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.烧两勺热油，油面冒烟后直接浇在辣椒碎上</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112431912-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.撒上熟芝麻拌匀</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011243NS-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.切好的藕片装进大点的容器里，撒上蒜蓉</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112434926-7.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.调入盐，醋，酱油，白糖，鸡精调味</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0112433563-8.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.淋入芝麻油，撒上小葱末拌匀即可</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1.藕不用去皮，表面刷洗干净直接煮就行。</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			切片后会比较方便煮，但是。。。切片煮出来的藕片和整节煮好再切片的口感真的差很多</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(84, 2, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113095233-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		猪肉：补肾、滋阴、益气</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		鸡蛋：润燥、增强免疫力、护眼明目</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					面粉250g</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					猪肉100g</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡蛋1个</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					豆腐干4块</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					胡萝卜1根</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					白萝卜1截</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					干黄花菜1小把</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					黄豆1/2杯</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					水适量</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113092J9-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.面粉中加入盐，搅匀后打入鸡蛋。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113093T2-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.一边加水、一边用筷子小心搅拌面粉。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113093033-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.搅拌至面粉呈大块雪片状。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011309C29-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.用手揉成面团，此时面团粗糙一些没有关系。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011309D32-5.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					5.盖上面盆，饧15分钟，重新揉面团，如此反复2到3次。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113094Q0-6.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					6.揉过3次的面团，已经变得非常光滑。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113091207-7.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					7.最后饧好的面团擀成0.5厘米厚的面片。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113093536-8.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					8.撒足量面粉，切成10厘米宽，叠在一起。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113092106-9.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					9.切成菱形块。。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01130a064-10.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					10.用双手拉住菱形块的两端，慢慢抻长、抻薄。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113093Z2-11.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					11.所有干货提前用温水泡发，全部臊子材料切成丁。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/01130aB1-12.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					12.锅烧热，放少许油，加入一大勺辣椒酱，炒匀后放入肉丁。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011309D64-13.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					13.待肉丁变色后，放入浸泡后的黄豆。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113094I1-14.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					14.加入木耳碎、黄花菜碎、香菇丁。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011309AJ-15.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					15.加入豆腐干，再加入少许酱油，少许水。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113093918-16.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					16.全部材料翻炒均匀，炒至收汁，盛出待用。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113093012-17.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					17.锅中加水，放入一大勺辣椒酱，加入胡萝卜丁和白萝卜丁。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113094135-18.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					18.水开后下入宽面，水再次烧开后继续煮3分钟，捞出面，拌上臊子即可。</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1．反复揉面团，不仅使面团变得光滑，且做出的面条更加筋道；</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2．面片一定要撒足量面粉，才能重叠起来，面粉量不够的话，容易粘连；</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			3．菱形块切好后及时散开，以防粘连；</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(85, 2, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113311308-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		大米：富含碳水化合物、富含锰</p>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		姜：降逆止呕、化痰止咳、散寒解表</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					大米100g</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡胸肉50g</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鲜香菇2朵</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					生菜叶3片</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					姜1小块</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					植物油5ml</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					盐少许</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					水适量</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113313b9-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.大米淘洗干净后清水浸泡30分钟，鲜香菇洗净切薄片，生菜洗净后用手撕成小片，姜切片</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113312253-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.鸡脯肉洗净，剁成碎末，用少许盐、淀粉和少许油拌匀后腌一下</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011331G57-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.锅中放入足量清水烧开，放入浸泡后的大米，再加入1小勺油，大火煮开后转小火继续煮30分钟，至米粥软烂</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0113311092-4.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					4.加入鸡肉迅速搅散，加入香菇片煮2分钟后关火，最后放入生菜，加盐调味即可</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			1.煮粥时加入少许油，能使煮成的粥米粒饱满，色泽鲜亮。</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			2.如果有鸡汤，骨头汤，用来代替清水煮粥，会让粥更香滑、醇厚。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0'),
(86, 3, '<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011642L42-0.jpg" style="margin: 40px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;" />\r\n<div class="introduction" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, 黑体, 楷体;">\r\n	<h3 style="margin: auto 40px; padding: 0px; height: 25px; line-height: 25px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		健康功效：</h3>\r\n	<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px;">\r\n		百合：安神、清心、润肺</p>\r\n	<table style="margin: 10px auto 20px; padding: 0px; width: 580px; height: 205px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-collapse: collapse; text-indent: 15px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n		<thead style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;">\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td border="0" colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					食材</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</thead>\r\n		<tbody style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					主料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					西芹</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					百合</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr class="collapse" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; background: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: bold;">\r\n				<td colspan="2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					辅料</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					盐</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					胡椒粉</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					鸡精</td>\r\n				<td style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 289px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); height: 40px;">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n	<div class="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011642G10-1.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					1.西芹洗净，斜切成小段。锅里水煮开，放入西芹焯水一分钟左右，捞出冲凉水沥干。百合去掉黑色部分，掰成小片，洗净沥干</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/011642M00-2.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					2.烧热锅，倒入油加热后，放焯过水的西芹，翻炒片刻</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 10px 0px 10px 50px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; width: 580px; height: 135px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(153, 153, 153);">\r\n				<img src="/uploads/allimg/171225/0116423920-3.jpg" style="margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; display: inline-block; clear: both; width: 190px; height: 125px; float: left;" />\r\n				<p style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; width: 350px; display: inline-block; font-size: 16px; float: left;">\r\n					3.放入百合，加盐和鸡精调味，快速翻炒入味，看到百合边缘变透明马上关火出锅</p>\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">\r\n			小贴士</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 5px 40px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);">\r\n			这是一道口清新的川菜，适合家庭聚餐。</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n', '', '', '0.0.0.0');
